Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.11,0:01:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Arthur konon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.49,0:01:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}memiliki toleransi tinggi terhadap racun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.77,0:01:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, bagaimana jika racun yang digunakan\Nsepuluh kali dosis mematikan?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.11,0:01:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lari!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.20,0:01:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tembak.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.02,0:02:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sial!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.73,0:02:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa tak ada pembunuh terampil\Nyang tersisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.11,0:02:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.61,0:02:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Manusia sungguh makhluk bodoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.70,0:02:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Robot jauh lebih bisa diandalkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.74,0:02:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya butuh Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.93,0:02:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Arthur, Pewaris Zetes muda yang sangat membenci\Nmanusia dan kebohongan,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}memiliki robot pelayan Marie
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.23,0:02:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan Marie-2 di sisinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.67,0:02:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berputar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.79,0:02:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pengisian dimulai.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.94,0:02:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.27,0:02:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini kesukaanmu, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.34,0:02:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak bilang itu favoritku.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.24,0:02:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong,\Nbagaimana kamu mengisi ulang dayamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.60,0:02:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin melihatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.09,0:03:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, Marie hanya manusia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.70,0:03:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika Arthur tahu,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.83,0:03:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie pasti akan dieksekusi di tempat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.37,0:03:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selesai sudah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie, semuanya sudah selesai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.42,0:03:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Manis sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.71,0:03:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Dia mudah tertipu.\N- Dia mudah tertipu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.70,0:03:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, Roy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.44,0:03:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bukankah keamanan rumah ini\Nterlalu longgar?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.97,0:03:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menurut saya, alasannya adalah\Npergantian para pekerja.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, mereka dipecat\Nbeberapa hari setelah bekerja.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.68,0:03:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur,\NAnda tampak lelah belakangan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.12,0:03:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa Anda tidak beristirahat\Ndari pekerjaan sesekali?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.01,0:03:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan sering melakukan hal yang sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.09,0:03:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski biasanya itu dengan wanita.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.45,0:03:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Istirahat...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.87,0:04:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika ada mode prioritas pesta,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.49,0:04:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}seharusnya ada mode kekasih juga, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.73,0:04:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak ada!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.98,0:04:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Muda mengharapkanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.89,0:04:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus bersikap layaknya pasangan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.57,0:04:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.02,0:04:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan, aku mencintai Tuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.12,0:04:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gagal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.87,0:04:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.21,0:04:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, dia akan mengatakan hal seperti itu\Nsaat dalam mode kekasih?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.75,0:04:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, jangan memanggilku Tuan\Nsaat kita berkencan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.01,0:04:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Arthur saja sudah cukup.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.30,0:04:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya mengerti.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.29,0:04:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu juga tak perlu terlalu sopan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.10,0:04:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, saya...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.29,0:04:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mengerti, Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.71,0:04:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat aku menjadi ahli bela diri,\Nguruku mengatakan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.15,0:04:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika mau menjadi lebih kuat,\Naku harus belajar dari yang kuat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.78,0:05:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika ingin masuk\Nke mode kekasih dengan sempurna,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.16,0:05:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku harus belajar dari sepasang kekasih dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.96,0:05:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sayang, mau minum teh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.15,0:05:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Baik, ayo.\N- Itu mereka!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.38,0:05:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Arthur, mau minum teh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.86,0:05:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.27,0:05:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ke mana kita harus pergi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.89,0:05:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau pergi ke toko itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.60,0:05:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus berada dekat\Ndengan pasangan itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.80,0:05:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku senang sekali!\NSayang, peluk aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.28,0:05:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cara Marie mengekspresikan dirinya\Ncukup intens.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.51,0:05:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya sungguh minta maaf...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.93,0:05:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.15,0:05:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku, Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.19,0:05:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini, Sayang.\NKatakan, "Ah..."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.45,0:05:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, aku juga...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.38,0:05:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Katakan, "Ah..."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.52,0:06:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini lezat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.67,0:06:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kali ini sukses.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.71,0:06:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, aku akan membalasnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.82,0:06:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini, Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.36,0:06:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu produk Zetes,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}baterai AA bertenaga tinggi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini bentuk baru KDRT?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.66,0:06:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wanita itu sepertinya sudah pasrah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.24,0:06:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami memilih rute yang sama\Ndengan pasangan tadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.38,0:06:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa ada perbedaan besar\Ndalam kemesraannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.72,0:06:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, Sayang, kamu tidak lelah?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.19,0:06:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sama sekali tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.57,0:06:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bisa menggendongmu ke ujung dunia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.76,0:06:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perahu kecil.\NBoleh juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.24,0:06:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur,\Nrobot akan rusak jika jatuh ke air.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.26,0:06:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya aku tak bisa berenang.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.77,0:06:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hampir lupa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.23,0:07:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika kamu rusak,\NRoy akan membawamu pergi lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia pasti trauma\Ndengan kejadian sebelumnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.51,0:07:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu cukup.\NTerima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.35,0:07:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, tutup matamu sebentar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.54,0:07:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa aku berpikir untuk naik kapal?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga punya hadiah untuk sayangku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.54,0:07:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hadiah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.36,0:07:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasanya seperti kekasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.49,0:07:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga akan menggunakannya\Nuntuk membalikkan keadaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.16,0:07:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cium.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.68,0:07:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak bisa melakukan itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.57,0:07:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan, ini untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.67,0:07:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.95,0:07:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini semanggi berdaun empat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.32,0:07:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuharap ini membawa kebahagiaan\Nbagi hatimu yang lelah, Tuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.83,0:07:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana bisa kuberikan rumput liar\Nseperti ini pada tuanku yang kaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.08,0:07:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hal seperti sampaâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.22,0:08:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semahal apa pun hadiahnya,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.65,0:08:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jika tidak berisi\Nperasaan tulus pemberinya,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.53,0:08:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}itu sama sekali tidak berharga.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.02,0:08:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu sebabnya aku sangat bahagia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.31,0:08:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie, boleh aku memegang tanganmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.12,0:08:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.73,0:08:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada banyak pasangan hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.37,0:08:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, kami tidak seperti pasangan lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.04,0:08:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan pasti akan menemukan\Npacar yang baik suatu hari nanti.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.85,0:08:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.41,0:08:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya, kami hanya pura-pura\Nmenjadi pasangan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.27,0:08:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, gerejanya di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.28,0:09:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pernah ke sini dengan orang tuaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.57,0:09:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, ini tempat penuh kenangan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.08,0:09:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.83,0:09:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.25,0:09:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.04,0:09:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh aku menciummu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.51,0:09:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cium?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.09,0:09:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku memang dalam mode kekasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.92,0:09:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, membiarkannya menciumku\Nadalah jawaban yang benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.98,0:09:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.57,0:09:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.83,0:09:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur, tunggu aku di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.07,0:09:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.47,0:10:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagus, kamu lawan yang kubutuhkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.59,0:10:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu siap menebus dosa-dosamu dan bertobat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.20,0:10:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lumayan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.77,0:10:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu pacar Arthur?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.10,0:10:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan, aku hanya pelayannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.98,0:10:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.39,0:10:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Melihat betapa dekatnya kalian,\Nkupikir kalian pasangan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.11,0:10:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lebih dari itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.91,0:10:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, semua itu tak ada hubungannya\Ndenganmu, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitukah?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.12,0:10:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia kuat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.74,0:10:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie, kamu baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.38,0:10:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan, tetaplah di tempatmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.50,0:10:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu lengah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.30,0:10:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu ada hubungannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.47,0:10:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena aku sangat mengagumimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.69,0:10:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sampai jumpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.29,0:11:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan jatuh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.40,0:11:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.05,0:11:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku.\NAku membiarkannya lolos.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.35,0:11:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entah itu mode kekasih\Natau hanya menjagamu,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.84,0:11:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku tak bisa melakukan apa pun\Ndengan benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.83,0:11:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal Tuan sedang menikmati libur...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.36,0:11:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.45,0:11:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan menyimpan ciuman sungguhannya\Nuntuk mode kekasih berikutnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.15,0:11:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.58,0:11:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mode kekasih menggunakan banyak baterai,\Njadi aku tak bisa sering menggunakannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.45,0:11:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.38,0:12:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Roy? Bisa jemput kami?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.01,0:12:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.17,0:12:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan apa-apa.\NHanya saja, Marie bersikap aneh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.68,0:12:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, siapa pria kemarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.81,0:12:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika melihatnya lagi,\Naku pasti akan menghabisi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.89,0:12:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan memperkenalkan\Nmurid pindahan kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.28,0:12:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini Noah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.67,0:12:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Senang bertemu kalian semua.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.57,0:12:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?\NDia pria yang kemarin...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.08,0:12:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mengandalkanmu, Noah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.56,0:12:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ujian pindah sekolah kita\Nsangat sulit, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.13,0:12:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Noah, kamu luar biasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.92,0:12:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ajari aku cara belajar lain kali.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.63,0:12:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Daripada itu, ayo kita adakan\Npesta penyambutan dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.09,0:13:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kedengarannya bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.51,0:13:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari lakukan itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.89,0:13:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus segera memberi tahu Tuan Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.52,0:13:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus memberitahunya
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.92,0:13:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bahwa seorang pembunuh\Npindah ke sekolah kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.65,0:13:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, kamu tidak datang\Nke pesta penyambutanku, Marie?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.16,0:13:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski aku mau datang,\Ntak akan ada yang mengundangku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.41,0:13:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin semua orang takut padamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.00,0:13:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu tak punya ekspresi, jadi,\Ntak ada yang tahu apa yang kamu pikirkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.03,0:13:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, hanya ekspresi seperti ini
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.48,0:13:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yang layak diuji dengan rasa sakit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.48,0:13:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku jatuh cinta pada pandangan pertama\Nkali terakhir melihatmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.57,0:13:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pria ini psikopat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.94,0:13:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu sudah melihat wajahku,\Ntapi masih muncul di hadapanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.40,0:13:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa tujuanmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.78,0:14:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku membawakanmu hadiah hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.76,0:14:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa ini akan membuatmu\Nsangat bahagia, Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.92,0:14:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.88,0:14:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu masa lalu yang Roy hapus untukku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.01,0:14:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ini masa kini?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.26,0:14:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.25,0:14:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini semua cinta dan waktu yang kuhabiskan\Nuntuk mengumpulkan data.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.05,0:14:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini hadiahku untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.98,0:14:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menyeramkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.20,0:14:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.19,0:14:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menyebut dirimu "pelayan robot"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.75,0:14:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu sungguh berbohong pada Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.42,0:14:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang kamu inginkan dariku?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.80,0:14:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya mau akrab denganmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.99,0:14:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, kamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.82,0:14:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.63,0:14:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang kamu mau dari pelayanku?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.25,0:14:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami melihat beberapa foto menarik.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.00,0:14:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Foto menarik?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.75,0:14:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur akan tahu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.25,0:15:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, itu menarik.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.74,0:15:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.81,0:15:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya Marie lebih menyukaiku\Ndaripada kamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.61,0:15:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, kamu!\NSingkirkan tangan kotormu darinya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.43,0:15:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie terlihat risi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.56,0:15:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie, apa kamu risi padaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.24,0:15:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga mau
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.06,0:15:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}berhubungan baik dengan teman sekelas ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.55,0:15:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena dia punya
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.32,0:15:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}banyak informasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.13,0:15:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie milikku sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.04,0:15:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu bercanda?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.23,0:15:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pasti kamu yang memberi\NMarie hasutan aneh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.97,0:15:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menantangmu berduel demi Marie!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.28,0:15:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.64,0:15:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, jika aku menang,\NMarie akan jadi milikku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.12,0:15:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika aku menang, kamu tak boleh\Nmendekatiku dan Marie lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.06,0:15:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Tunggu!\N- Tunggu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.17,0:15:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayam?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.77,0:16:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tangkap mereka!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.23,0:16:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa, Toby?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.32,0:16:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Arthur!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.46,0:16:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tujuh ayam dari Klub Riset\NEkologi Hewan kabur!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.71,0:16:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana jika yang menangkap ayam\Nyang terbanyak, dia menang?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.46,0:16:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik, lagi pula, aku akan menang.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.94,0:16:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benarkah?\NItu bagus!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.86,0:16:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Totalnya ada tujuh ayam.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.99,0:16:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik, mari mulai kontes menangkap ayamnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.15,0:16:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika ini kompetisi mereka,\NTuan Arthur punya kesempatan untuk menang.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.46,0:16:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik, aku menangkapmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.08,0:16:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur sangat keren\Nkarena membuat ayam mematuhinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.47,0:16:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga mau tertangkap olehnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.93,0:16:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Para gadis itu mengikuti Arthur\Nke mana pun dia pergi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.99,0:16:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hewan itu luar biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.99,0:16:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak seperti manusia,\Nmereka tak bisa bicara atau berbohong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.50,0:16:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seberapa besar kamu membenci manusia?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.36,0:17:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.80,0:17:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini yang ketiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.81,0:17:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur, izinkan saya membantumu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu tak perlu sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.33,0:17:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini duel dengan mempertaruhkan\Nharga diri pria.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.98,0:17:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie, kumohon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.34,0:17:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maukah kamu menurut\Ndan membiarkanku melindungimu kali ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.66,0:17:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tadi itu ayam.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.84,0:17:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, aku akan menghubungimu\Njika menangkapnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.41,0:17:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.74,0:17:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong, ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.57,0:17:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih atas bantuan kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.67,0:17:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meminta bantuan teman-temanmu\Nitu tidak adil.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagian tak ada aturan\Naku tak boleh meminta bantuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.33,0:17:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, kamu di sini selama ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.42,0:17:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang, terbanglah ke pelukanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.45,0:17:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayam-ayamku yang manis!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.66,0:17:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia mungkin bisa menipu manusia\Ntentang fakta bahwa dia psikopat gila,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.35,0:17:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi dia tak bisa menipu hewan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.85,0:18:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa boleh buat?\NAku akan menggunakan itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.05,0:18:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik, biar kutunjukkan cinta.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.47,0:18:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia sungguh menggunakan alat pembunuhan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.61,0:18:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia menangkap tiga, seperti Tuan Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.42,0:18:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Noah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.08,0:18:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kudengar ada ayam\Ndi kebun depan kantin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.68,0:18:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akhirnya tiba waktu bagi kita\Nuntuk bertarung.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.38,0:18:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika aku menangkap ayam ini,\NMarie akan menjadi milikku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.48,0:18:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, Marie milikku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.14,0:18:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cepat sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.12,0:18:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ke mana perginya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.40,0:18:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.65,0:18:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika terus begini, Tuan Arthur akan kalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.16,0:18:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Satu-satunya hal yang bisa kulakukan\Nuntuk Tuan Arthur adalah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.92,0:19:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur, di belakangmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.62,0:19:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur, tolong menang.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.93,0:19:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku jatuh.\NAku tak boleh jatuh ke air!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.03,0:19:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada yang jatuh ke kolam!\NItu pelayan Arthur!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.13,0:19:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Andai aku cukup kuat\Nuntuk bertarung melawan semuanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.72,0:20:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.75,0:20:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.96,0:20:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan segera memanggil Roy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.98,0:20:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie, mungkin\Nkamu tak bisa mendengarku lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.43,0:20:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tangan Tuan Arthur gemetar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.49,0:20:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak bisa hidup tanpamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.42,0:20:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku yakin orang ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.97,0:20:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}selemah atau tak berguna apa pun aku,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.24,0:20:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}pasti akan melihatku\Nsebagai orang yang dia butuhkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.64,0:20:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.64,0:20:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya baik-baik saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.04,0:20:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.61,0:20:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, Tuan Arthur, duelnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.28,0:20:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Murid pindahan menang!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.90,0:20:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini jasmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.78,0:20:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pemenangnya sudah ditentukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.47,0:21:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur kalah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.26,0:21:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, Arthur menang.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.79,0:21:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia meninggalkan duel penting\Nuntuk menyelamatkan gadis itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.68,0:21:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu keren sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.42,0:21:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?\NKamu tampak tak senang.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.98,0:21:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana kalau kita anggap ini seri?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.11,0:21:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku selamat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.24,0:21:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku memberi tahu Tuan Muda\Nkamu tidak lama di dalam air,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.40,0:21:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jadi tak perlu perawatan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.22,0:21:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya apa yang kamu lakukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.47,0:21:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.47,0:22:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tampaknya Arthur yang butuh perawatan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.20,0:23:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie, mulai sekarang,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.20,0:23:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sendirian seumur hidupmu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.02,0:23:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sendirian seumur hidupmu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.91,0:23:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}paling cocok untukmu.
